    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your disciple of the hand class feature also applies to all shields, and to all primarily-metal armor and shields. When crafting such items, you can increase the price by 25% to increase the item's Hardness by 1 and its Hit Points by an amount equal to half your level (minimum 1). You also treat metal shields as being in your gift's preferred weapons list.</p><p>In addition, you become trained in all armor; when your proficiency rank in unarmored defense increases beyond trained, this proficiency is increased to the same rank.</p>",
